    <intro>&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Session 2.3 will meet on Nov. 22, 2024 at 2 PM ET/11 AM PT.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Session 2.3 log in information:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://air-org.zoom.us/j/96080108867?pwd=mOU19gZhDZVIWCO3TUkmWucS5eVGiS.1"&gt;https://air-org.zoom.us/j/96080108867?pwd=mOU19gZhDZVIWCO3TUkmWucS5eVGiS.1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;Prior to the session, download the Handouts folder. Make sure that you have the following handouts available for the session. If possible, print out these handouts:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://lincs.ed.gov/sites/default/files/2024-05/Fixing%20the%20Furnace.pdf" target="_blank" title="https://lincs.ed.gov/sites/default/files/2024-05/Fixing%20the%20Furnace.pdf"&gt;Fixing the Furnace&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://lincs.ed.gov/sites/default/files/2024-05/Planning%20for%20Productive%20Mathematical%20Discussions.pdf" target="_blank" title="Planning for Productive Mathematical Discussions"&gt;Planning for Productive Mathematical Discussions&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Session 2.3 Agenda&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p dir="ltr"&gt;In Session 2.3, we will discuss the importance of explicit planning as you plan to facilitate meaningful and productive mathematical discourse. You will learn about specific instructional techniques that support high-quality mathematical discourse, and through working with your colleagues on a task, you will have an opportunity to practice planning for discourse together.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Launch&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Session 2.2 Debrief&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Session 2.3 Learning Objectives&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Explore&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Planning for Mathematical Discourse: Fixing the Furnace&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Summarize&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Big Ideas From Session 2.3&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Preview of Session 2.4&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center; "&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please note that your training facilitator will manually mark this activity complete if you attend the session.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 0.9375rem;"&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;</intro>
